# Repository Rules (Simplified)
# =============================================================================
# Purpose: Lightweight guidance for this repo. No branch or agent restrictions.
# =============================================================================

## General
- Follow user instructions and repository conventions.
- Keep changes focused and avoid unrelated edits.
- Avoid destructive commands unless explicitly requested.
- Do not commit unless the user asks.

## Quality
- Prefer clear, maintainable code.
- Use existing patterns and utilities when available.
- Run lint/tests when requested or after substantial changes if feasible.

## Protected Files
- Ask before editing if uncertain or high-impact.

